- Product Ordering Userflow
Customer Orders product -> Finance Manager Approves Payment -> Inventory Manager Allocates to dispatch Manager -> Dispatch manager checks in the order the allocates it to a driver -> The driver logs in then starts delivery and marks it as complete -> Go back to dispatch manager and mark delivery complete -> Go to customer page and confirm delivery recieved


- Services booking userflow
Customer books for a services -> Finance Manager Approves the service -> Service manager logs in and allocates supervisor the service -> Login as suppervisor accept task then Allocated Recyclers for the service -> Login as the allocated worker -> Accept task -> Request for materials -> Login as inventory manager and approve tools requested -> Login to worked again and end task -> Log back in as supervisor and mark as complete -> Customer logs in again and marks as complete -> Go back to suppervisor dashboard and confirm the work is in the completed tasks


